{"tha-ap423:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap423:0.2":"Sakimsammajjakavagga ","tha-ap423:0.3":"Sakimsammajjakattheraapadana ","tha-ap423:1.1":"“Vipassino bhagavato, ","tha-ap423:1.2":"patalim bodhimuttamam; ","tha-ap423:1.3":"Disvava tam padapaggam, ","tha-ap423:1.4":"tattha cittam pasadayim. ","tha-ap423:2.1":"Sammajjanim gahetvana, ","tha-ap423:2.2":"bodhim sammajji tavade; ","tha-ap423:2.3":"Sammajjitvana tam bodhim, ","tha-ap423:2.4":"avandim patalim aham. ","tha-ap423:3.1":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap423:3.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","tha-ap423:3.3":"Namassamano tam bodhim, ","tha-ap423:3.4":"ganchim patikutim aham. ","tha-ap423:4.1":"Tadimaggena gacchami, ","tha-ap423:4.2":"saranto bodhimuttamam; ","tha-ap423:4.3":"Ajagaro mam pilesi, ","tha-ap423:4.4":"ghorarupo mahabbalo. ","tha-ap423:5.1":"Asanne me katam kammam, ","tha-ap423:5.2":"phalena tosayi mamam; ","tha-ap423:5.3":"Kalevaram me gilati, ","tha-ap423:5.4":"devaloke ramamaham. ","tha-ap423:6.1":"Anavilam mama cittam, ","tha-ap423:6.2":"visuddham pandaram sada; ","tha-ap423:6.3":"Sokasallam na janami, ","tha-ap423:6.4":"cittasantapanam mama. ","tha-ap423:7.1":"Kuttham gando kilaso ca, ","tha-ap423:7.2":"apamaro vitacchika; ","tha-ap423:7.3":"Daddu kandu ca me natthi, ","tha-ap423:7.4":"phalam sammajjanayidam. ","tha-ap423:8.1":"Soko ca paridevo ca, ","tha-ap423:8.2":"hadaye me na vijjati; ","tha-ap423:8.3":"Abhantam ujukam cittam, ","tha-ap423:8.4":"phalam sammajjanayidam. ","tha-ap423:9.1":"Samadhisu na majjami, ","tha-ap423:9.2":"visadam hoti manasam; ","tha-ap423:9.3":"Yam yam samadhimicchami, ","tha-ap423:9.4":"so so sampajjate mamam. ","tha-ap423:10.1":"Rajaniye na rajjami, ","tha-ap423:10.2":"atho dussaniyesu ca; ","tha-ap423:10.3":"Mohaniye na muyhami, ","tha-ap423:10.4":"phalam sammajjanayidam. ","tha-ap423:11.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap423:11.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap423:11.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap423:11.4":"phalam sammajjanayidam. ","tha-ap423:12.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap423:12.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap423:12.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap423:12.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap423:13.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap423:13.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap423:13.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap423:13.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap423:14.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap423:14.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap423:14.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap423:14.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap423:15.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sakimsammajjako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap423:16.1":"Sakimsammajjakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}